data.description: Immaculate executive home in the prestigious Ascot Ridge neighborhood.  Everything you could possibly want in this beautiful, mint condition 4 bedroom home.  The kitchen is well-planned and spacious with a large center island, a wet bar, custom tile back splash and lots of storage with custom-built cabinets.  This home features two bedrooms on the main level including the master bedroom.  Each room has a private bath and an additional half bath for a total of 4.5 baths.  The master suite includes tray ceilings, his & her walk-in closets, his & her vanities, private water closet, whirlpool tub and separate large shower!   Two additional spacious and oversized bedrooms with private baths and sitting/play areas are located on the second floor.  The sun room with slide doors throughout is perfect year round and features a split system for heating and cooling when needed.  Tons of storage and built in closets throughout the home.  This home has it all including hardwood floors throughout the main floor, a 3-car side entry garage with plenty of room for oversized cars, storage and workshop along with HVAC system with foot pedal sweep system. Completing this luxury home you will find 9' ceilings throughout, detailed trim work and lots more! Zoned for award winning Lex/Rich 5 schools! Enjoy all the neighborhood amenities such as the pool, tennis courts and walking trails. Convenient to shopping and restaurants. Awesome home!!!
